# Deploying to GitHub

**Repository:** https://github.com/HRBlackwood/TTG-website-new.git  
**Branch:** `main`  
**Shell:** PowerShell — use `;` to chain commands, NOT `&&`

## Deploy Steps

```powershell
git add .
git commit -m "your message here"
git push origin main
```

## If Push is Denied (Wrong Account)

Clear cached credentials, then push again:

```powershell
cmdkey /delete:git:https://github.com; git push origin main
```

A browser window will open — sign in as **HRBlackwood**.

